      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.75761-15/482927284_18330144379095126_980463994261929195_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_s1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=105&amp;ig_cache_key=MzU4MDAyMzAyNDY1OTMzNDM0Mg%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTQ0MC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=D61PT5kzb3wQ7kNvwE79ujQ&amp;_nc_oc=AdoKn0fNhnHlE2sGhWPtk_n0SjD0LR1Vnc5mv5jHNXn15m21Bzbw05VNTdOpkKFcrHE&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=C3WV2qxIuE6Yt1tuomrbxg&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_Afw6iUy9htZwaijWpgFPqu1KAUBqLzKkJPeBNARGAP-rJg&amp;oe=69C9B9DB" alt="Instagram billede fra @metahaven" /></p><p><strong>@metahaven</strong></p><p>it’s been a huge joy to work with @n_a_l_b_a_n_d_i_a_n on the cover for his latest album, “studies on resonance and dissonance” - a project armen created closely together with @jingy.teo . armen nalbandian’s work brings motives from jazz and classical piano into a sphere of improvisation and noise, combining (in a way) satie with ruins and far beyond. thank you armen and jing 🔥🧶💫</p>]]></description>
